_sText:
This is the first beta version of Goodfellas Arena X.

There are no known bugs but if any are found please post here or e-mail me at deal@thehightower.net.

On top of the roofs walk off the side and you will be teleported to the adjacent rooftop. The two rooftops not by spawns also have teleports at their rear. To get to the balconies from the bottom walk into the x on the botton of the map.

All teleports have been optimized so that if someone stands on the target of the teleport there is 80% less chance players will be teleported into each other.

Has a custom soundscape.

The sky box texture was not made by me but by hipshot (www.zfight.com).

The beta2 version is already in the works so please post comments and ideas as they may make it into the map.
